	border of the dialog. Make "Yes" the default action.

	* keydeletedlg.c (delete_ok, delete_cancel, delete_destroy): Removed.
	A GtkDialog does not need callbacks.
	(gpa_delete_dialog_run): Use a GtkDialog.

