	gpa_set_default_key

	* gpa.c (global_defaultKey):
	(gpa_default_key):
	(gpa_set_default_key): Turn global_defaultKey into a static
	varible default_key and introduce gpa_set_default_key and
	gpa_default_key to set and get its value

